arguments.name: Values
arguments.description: An array or a reference to cells that contain numbers. These numbers represent a series of payments (negative values) and income (positive values) occurring at regular periods.

arguments.name: Finance_rate
arguments.description: The interest rate you pay on the money used in the cash flows.

arguments.name: Reinvest_rate
arguments.description: The interest rate you receive on the cash flows as you reinvest them.
